java.lang.Object
ca.openosp.openo.integration.fhir.builder.AbstractFhirMessageBuilder<T>
Direct Known Subclasses:
FhirBundleBuilder, FhirCommunicationBuilder
public abstract class AbstractFhirMessageBuilder<T extends org.hl7.fhir.dstu3.model.BaseResource> extends Object
Builds a FHIR message with the given OscarFhirResources.
